{"tid":280531,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎討論下各大main contractor 比d fresh grad做參考","createTime":"2017-06-12T07:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T17:31:43.000Z","uid":69215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36a16dd0454873c3c12b097485ad3a01b4b46bb4","tid":280531,"uid":69215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:01:19.000Z","msg":"臨近ive 仔同八大院校畢業，各位巴打講下自己係唔同contractor入面做既經驗，比d fresh grad做下參考。<br />\nMain con比較出名既有：中國老 中國路x 俊仔記 十三力 build Kinging 寶加 保Y 新輝 新世界 南豐 精進 有利 新昌<br />\n<br />\n我剩係做過中國老新xx, 中國老就幾個句講曬，多野做有同事試過三日冇返屋企，人事複雜因爲有阿公，但福利就樣樣有d，人工出手唔底<br />\n新世界，暫時咁多間main con 福利最好，多野做但對員工真係唔錯由其花紅。<br />\n保y人工不過不失，好撚多野做入去基本上就一腳踢，但出返黎就一個打三個。"},{"pid":"09d84d1450ccef69a6bbcb08e6987f7e503dbf25","tid":280531,"uid":69215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:17:45.000Z","msg":"Push fresh grad 有咩想問可以係到問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5b1af74272154d19d56abbd51891709d1946e5","tid":280531,"uid":46722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:58:10.000Z","msg":"冇金門份？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaa66748293986ae3bb287676d079a3710c94be","tid":280531,"uid":102212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:01:39.000Z","msg":"Contractor係唔係少啲資源去幫fresh grad考scheme A架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1107e5d24d254d7e61fe7e523025f84980b5e460","tid":280531,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"禮X X門呢？"},{"pid":"d6927c70233e521739a48e78c43267694db5836a","tid":280531,"uid":69215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇金門份？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打唔曬啦太多contractor 重有禮頓 其士 SFK 建業"},{"pid":"dae89396a3af49bd0c34d3a119089d67b626fdc0","tid":280531,